B.y3=new A.d0(u.j,"Hello, my name is Edoardo Fabrizio De Iovanna, a developer with Italian-Brazilian roots.\nI was born in Milan, Italy, and as a child, I moved to Olgiate Comasco.\nWhen I was 10, my family moved to Brazil, settling in Taiobeiras, Minas Gerais.\nAt the age of 13, I went to Aracaju, Sergipe, where I finished high school and started my degree in Information Systems.\nDuring my studies, I discovered my passion for mobile development, exploring languages \u200b\u200bsuch as C++, C# and Java.\nIn 2020, I returned to Taiobeiras and specialized in Flutter, a framework that I use to create innovative cross-platform experiences.\nI am currently looking for opportunities to grow professionally and contribute to ambitious technology projects.",B.ha,B.fE)
B.y2=new A.d0("assets/images/certificates.png","Earning certifications is a key part of my career path and dedication to continuous learning.\nI have attended courses and workshops on programming languages \u200b\u200band agile methodologies.\nThese include certifications in C#, Java, Python, Flutter, and Unreal Engine, as well as advanced development tools. \nEach certificate reflects my commitment to translating theory into practice, underlining my desire to excel in providing high-quality software solutions.",B.ar,B.fD)
B.y1=new A.d0("assets/images/work.png","During my studies, I developed some personal projects that allowed me to deepen my skills in mobile development.\nBelow are two of my main projects:\n\nBooks Catalog:\n\u2726 A native Android app for managing and organizing books, developed using Java and Android Studio.\nBookify:\n\u2726 A Flutter app for discovering and cataloging books, designed to offer a fluid experience across platforms.\n\nBoth projects can be found on my GitHub.",B.ar,B.fF)
B.y0=new A.d0("assets/images/game_hobby.jpeg","In my free time, I enjoy immersing myself in virtual worlds, exploring new stories and experiencing new challenges.\nTechnology offers me the opportunity to test myself in ever new and stimulating contexts.\nI don't just play familiar titles, but I'm always looking for new experiences and challenges.\nI love discovering innovative and original games that make me think critically and develop new skills.\nMy passion for video games is not just for fun, but also a way to train my mind and broaden my horizons.",B.ar,B.fC)
B.y9=new A.d0("assets/images/music_hobby.jpeg","In addition to the activities already mentioned, music holds a special place in my life.\nIn particular, I enjoy playing the recorder, an instrument that I find relaxing and versatile, in addition to its soft and delicate sound.\nI enjoy the challenge of learning new songs and improving my skills.",B.ar,null)
